Nature of this software
-----------------------
This repository is a thin client for the Vaquill backend API. It contains the
Google Docs add-on (Apps Script server code and Svelte sidebar) only. It does
not include, and does not grant any license to, the Vaquill backend, models,
prompts, corpus, or hosted services. Running it requires a Vaquill account, or
your own backend that implements a compatible API.
